metadata.name: The "Bootsy Cyborg"
metadata.description: The Power Of The One created the Bootsy Cyborg as an extension of itself to be all that is, everything that was & always will be. The Bootsy Cyborg was now freed from the box of limited space & time. Bootsyâ€™s human soul and spirit lives on through the digital uploading of himself while getting rid of the extra baggage that has always affected his time & space. His mission is to connect all citizens of the Universe to the Power Of The One. By doing so you will be recreated in a new frame, into a new world of being! Phase 2 is on you!
